/#
   A structure used to identify a portfolio in a message.
 #/
record FpML5.reporting.PortfolioReferenceBase {
  # An identifier that is unique for each portfolio-level request, and which can be used to group together the individual messages in the portfolio request.
  portfolioName : string?

}

portfolioName.Doc: An identifier that is unique for each portfolio-level request, and which can be used to group together the individual messages in the portfolio request.
